    {"code": "HRM-4", "name": "An onboarding checklist is maintained and followed for all new hires", "description": "A well-defined onboarding checklist exists for all new hires. The checklist ensures that the new hire is assigned appropriate access to information systems based on the role by the system owners, allocated the right assets, and undergoes the right training and orientation workshops."},
